	‚Ä¢ PVC issues
	‚Ä¢ Node selector mismatch
	‚Ä¢ Affinity constraints
	‚Ä¢ Security restrictions
	‚Ä¢ ResourceQuota enforcement
	‚Ä¢ GPU & ephemeral storage limits

